com.koverse.sdk.annotation

Annotation Type StringParameter


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface StringParameter
    Describes a string (text) parameter for an extensible Koverse component. Fields annotated with this annotation will have the values supplied by the user injected into them after object construction.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String defaultValue
      The default value for this parameter.
      String description
      The human readable description of this parameter.
      String groupName
      The human readable group name of this parameter.
      String id
      The unique identifier for this parameter.
      String name
      The human readable name of this parameter.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean hideInput
      Whether or not the user interface should hide the input entered in by the user, such as for a password.
      boolean required
      Whether or not the user is required to give this parameter a value.
